dotfiles
========

May these be useful.


Compatibility
-------------

Unless otherwise noted, these confs and scripts should work correctly
on OpenBSD-current, with versions tagged corresponding with each
release.

I test things periodically on the latest versions of Fedora and
CentOS Linux; but if package versions fall behind, I typically roll
forward on OpenBSD, and wait to update installed Linux copies until
after an OS upgrade.


Testing
-------

Besides daily use, scripts should pass the following linters:

- shell scripts: https://github.com/koalaman/shellcheck
